\begin_layout Subsection
Spontaneous Emission
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Here we show that time-local behavior of Ehrenfest dynamics in the 
\emph on
weak coupling limit
\emph default
 can be approximated by an exponential decay with a time-dependent instantaneous
 decay rate.
 We can also derive an analytical expression of Ehrenfest dynamics for spontaneo
us emission in 1D.
\end_layout

