\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset

 can be obtained by 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left[\frac{1}{2}\ln\left(1+\Delta P\right)-\frac{1}{2}\ln\left(1-\Delta P\right)\right]_{t}^{t+\tau}\approx-k_{\mathrm{FGR}}\frac{\tau}{2}.
\end{equation}

\end_inset

 Hence, we conclude an analytical form of Ehrenfest dynamics for 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{2}$
\end_inset

,
